@DATABASE "Fantasy World Dizzy"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - F - Fantasy World Dizzy"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - F
                   ====================================

                            Fantasy World Dizzy
                            ===================


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(63001,0)"}          63001,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(42481,255)"}          42481,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
